snippet.title: Adele: Following the Signs Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Adele: Following the Signs Video Game is now available to buy on Steam.  A 2.5D puzzle platform indie game with 19 levels of challenging obstacles, monster bosses and mutant plants!  All of the art and music in this game is original!  Play Now!  

Link: http://store.steampowered.com/app/457980
